Sentencas: The double perovskites Sr2-xCaxMgMoO6-delta with x = 0, 0.25, and 0.5 were obtained by combustion of organometallic precursors and were shown to have a tetragonal structure with the crystalline lattice parameters a = b = 5.569, c = 7.923, 7.899, 7.885 , respectively.
Titulo: The physical properties and electrochemical performance of Ca-doped Sr2MgMoO6-δ as perspective anode for solid oxide fuel cells
